OL,3,CPrince George turns 13 in new birthday
OL,4,Cportrait as he prepares to start Eton
OL,6,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales have
OL,7,Fshared a new picture of their eldest
OL,8,Fson George to celebrate his 13th
OL,9,Fbirthday.
OL,11,FIn the image, published on Instagram
OL,12,Fand X, Prince George can be seen
OL,13,Fwearing a dark-coloured suit and an
OL,14,Fopen-necked white shirt after
OL,15,Freturning from last month's Trooping
OL,16,Fthe Colour.
OL,18,F"Happy 13th Birthday, George!" the
OL,19,Fimage was captioned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
