OL,3,CPrince George turns 13 in new birthday
OL,4,Cportrait as he prepares to start Eton
OL,6,FThe portrait was taken by Matt
OL,7,FPorteous, who is William and Kate's go-
OL,8,Fto photographer for family
OL,9,Fcelebrations, and was also reshared by
OL,10,Fthe King and Queen Camilla.
OL,12,FPrince George Alexander Louis was born
OL,13,Fin the private Lindo Wing of St Mary's
OL,14,FHospital, Paddington, London, at
OL,15,F4.24pm on July 22 2013, weighing 8lb
OL,16,F6oz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
