OL,3,CPrince George turns 13 in new birthday
OL,4,Cportrait as he prepares to start Eton
OL,6,FThis year's birthday is a significant
OL,7,Fone for him, as he will start at Eton
OL,8,FCollege in September, following in the
OL,9,Ffootsteps of his father Prince William
OL,10,Fand uncle, Prince Harry.
OL,12,FPupils start the historic private
OL,13,Fschool, where fees are around #65,000
OL,14,Fa year, when they turn 13.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
